88
00:04:50,168 --> 00:04:51,192
Because ever since I was blind

89
00:04:51,369 --> 00:04:54,167
Radio's my connection to the world

90
00:04:55,540 --> 00:04:56,302
Hello

91
00:04:57,375 --> 00:04:58,307
