98
00:05:13,090 --> 00:05:14,751
And often jokes over it

99
00:05:15,426 --> 00:05:18,691
I've notice. Usually you don't talk much

100
00:05:19,463 --> 00:05:20,623
Except when you talk...

101
00:05:20,798 --> 00:05:21,787
