120
00:06:13,217 --> 00:06:14,684
Do you want to go?

121
00:06:15,119 --> 00:06:17,883
No, the exam. I don't want to flunk it

122
00:06:18,823 --> 00:06:20,188
That's true

123
00:06:21,292 --> 00:06:22,850
Never mind, next time then

124
00:06:23,694 --> 00:06:26,322
After all, failure is the mom of success

125
00:06:35,072 --> 00:06:37,165
Sorry, I'm sorry, Onion...

126
00:06:38,009 --> 00:06:40,375
So sorry, I'm late again

127
00:06:40,511 --> 00:06:41,808
Have you been waiting long?

128
00:06:41,946 --> 00:06:43,538
Sorry

129
00:06:45,549 --> 00:06:47,312
It is the thirtieth time

130
00:06:47,451 --> 00:06:48,543
she cuts my hair

131
00:06:49,220 --> 00:06:51,484
I'm not too greedy

132
00:06:51,923 --> 00:06:54,858
Just wish it happen...

133
00:06:54,992 --> 00:06:57,790
863 times in my life

134
00:06:58,496 --> 00:06:59,929
What are you thinking? Fallen asleep?

135
00:07:00,731 --> 00:07:02,858
Did you have the apples I bought you?

136
00:07:09,507 --> 00:07:12,305
You remember my birthday!

137
00:07:12,877 --> 00:07:14,401
I just told you once

138
00:07:15,012 --> 00:07:15,910
Thank you!

139
00:07:19,083 --> 00:07:21,574
Someone said

140
00:07:21,719 --> 00:07:22,981
I'm clumsy today

141
00:07:23,287 --> 00:07:24,447
No? Really?

142
00:07:24,822 --> 00:07:25,686
If people has...

143
00:07:25,823 --> 00:07:27,222
