145
00:07:29,460 --> 00:07:31,052
If you get a lousy body,

146
00:07:31,228 --> 00:07:32,525
you'll get a good brain

147
00:07:33,030 --> 00:07:33,962
If you are not pretty,

148
00:07:34,098 --> 00:07:35,258
you'll get a nice voice

149
00:07:35,833 --> 00:07:37,391
Why I have nothing,

150
00:07:38,002 --> 00:07:39,492
