158
00:08:06,097 --> 00:08:06,995
And you won't...

159
00:08:07,131 --> 00:08:08,257
tell my secrets

160
00:08:09,667 --> 00:08:11,134
So...

161
00:08:11,268 --> 00:08:13,998
I feel very safe with you

162
00:08:14,772 --> 00:08:18,208
You are the only one I can talk to

163
00:08:20,644 --> 00:08:23,078
If you don't want to listen,

164
00:08:23,214 --> 00:08:24,203
tell me

165
00:08:24,915 --> 00:08:27,543
You really don't?

166
00:08:28,386 --> 00:08:30,820
Don't like it?

167
00:08:32,089 --> 00:08:33,784
Don't rub your nose!

168
00:08:34,625 --> 00:08:37,822
I'm just kidding

169
00:08:43,601 --> 00:08:44,727
Did you hear?

170
00:08:45,036 --> 00:08:47,004
I heard it again last night

171
00:08:47,405 --> 00:08:48,064
Don't know why

172
00:08:48,205 --> 00:08:49,695
Every time I hear it

173
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:53,071
I feel relax

174
00:08:53,744 --> 00:08:55,211
Dr. Woo said he could play it

175
00:08:55,479 --> 00:08:57,447
But it's not him, I'm sure

176
00:08:57,948 --> 00:08:59,575
He can't play that well

177
00:09:02,787 --> 00:09:05,620
Sometimes I want to find out

178
00:09:06,023 --> 00:09:07,547
