193
00:09:49,900 --> 00:09:51,197
Give me a call

194
00:09:51,335 --> 00:09:53,701
Let's chat in the air

195
00:09:54,138 --> 00:09:56,868
Hoping that you can be relieved...

196
00:09:57,508 --> 00:09:58,975
From any distress and problem

197
00:11:04,942 --> 00:11:07,570
I can play sax since small

198
00:11:08,179 --> 00:11:10,841
