199
00:11:11,382 --> 00:11:13,680
I played sax with him together

200
00:11:14,185 --> 00:11:17,086
I had performance in blind school too

201
00:11:17,855 --> 00:11:20,016
Ever since Autumn says she likes sax,

202
00:11:20,457 --> 00:11:22,925
