205
00:11:28,933 --> 00:11:30,730
Not to...

206
00:11:30,868 --> 00:11:32,529
mention me

207
00:11:33,537 --> 00:11:35,767
Better not screw up her dream

208
00:11:35,906 --> 00:11:38,204
Or she might stop...

209
00:11:38,342 --> 00:11:39,809
cutting my hair

210
00:11:48,552 --> 00:11:49,746
