211
00:11:49,887 --> 00:11:51,912
Got to go, I'm late. Bye!

212
00:12:06,537 --> 00:12:07,367
Is it good?

213
00:12:08,839 --> 00:12:10,932
You are the first one to say that

214
00:12:11,542 --> 00:12:13,476
Weird! Why they don't like it?

215
00:12:14,912 --> 00:12:16,607
I know, you are always on my side

216
00:12:17,982 --> 00:12:19,074
Did you hear it?

217
00:12:20,517 --> 00:12:21,609
The sax

