249
00:14:05,989 --> 00:14:07,456
How great!

250
00:14:08,192 --> 00:14:09,159
And the second one?

251
00:14:13,764 --> 00:14:15,891
Come on, say it

252
00:14:16,934 --> 00:14:18,902
Come on. It tickles

