256
00:14:39,056 --> 00:14:41,081
Move, move... right...

257
00:14:42,960 --> 00:14:46,896
Turn right, right...

258
00:14:47,998 --> 00:14:49,522
Straight down, get move

259
00:14:49,700 --> 00:14:51,668
No, no, back up, back up...

260
00:14:52,636 --> 00:14:54,331
Move on, I'm late!

261
00:14:55,038 --> 00:14:56,471
Oh, my god! It'll hit!

262
00:14:58,542 --> 00:14:59,770
Straight down

263
00:15:00,244 --> 00:15:01,438
Getting off ahead, thank you

264
00:15:03,814 --> 00:15:05,338
Thanks, Onion

265
00:15:17,795 --> 00:15:18,523
"Wait for me"

266
00:15:40,050 --> 00:15:41,210
You look great, Onion

267
00:15:46,290 --> 00:15:48,781
