272
00:16:45,082 --> 00:16:47,209
Mr. Young, please queue here

273
00:16:57,094 --> 00:16:58,118
This way

274
00:16:59,096 --> 00:17:01,257
What? It's my friend. Bothers you?

275
00:17:21,084 --> 00:17:22,608
Jackpot? You are the sixty billion human

276
00:17:22,753 --> 00:17:24,118
travelling from the Earth...

277
00:17:24,254 --> 00:17:25,653
to the Polaris

278
00:17:26,123 --> 00:17:28,114
