589
00:39:10,826 --> 00:39:11,918
No parking ahead. Can't go in

590
00:39:14,163 --> 00:39:14,891
Three hundreds!

591
00:39:17,499 --> 00:39:18,227
How far ahead?

592
00:39:19,368 --> 00:39:22,826
Not far. Take this way

593
00:39:32,014 --> 00:39:32,878
What's up?

594
00:39:37,586 --> 00:39:38,678
Can I ask you...

595
00:39:39,855 --> 00:39:42,187
What happen to my little sister who...

596
00:39:42,324 --> 00:39:44,315
...used to be so strong?

597
00:39:45,461 --> 00:39:48,555
Thanks for the compliments. I'm fine

598
00:39:50,900 --> 00:39:52,162
Okay

599
00:39:54,036 --> 00:39:56,004
Strong. Is it a compliment?

600
00:39:56,438 --> 00:39:58,906
I thought it meant bad tempered

601
00:40:03,245 --> 00:40:05,577
Come when you want to talk

602
00:40:10,586 --> 00:40:13,111
Let me... stay still, Your Majesty

603
00:40:13,422 --> 00:40:15,117
Just treat me as Queen later

604
00:40:16,859 --> 00:40:17,917
Dr. Woo?

605
00:40:18,060 --> 00:40:19,391
Good guess! You are here

606
00:40:20,195 --> 00:40:22,561
I am just dropping by

607
00:40:22,698 --> 00:40:23,995
and see if you're here

608
00:40:24,133 --> 00:40:25,623
And you are

609
00:40:25,935 --> 00:40:27,027
Drop by?

610
00:40:28,103 --> 00:40:30,298
It takes at least two-hour to come here

611
00:40:30,439 --> 00:40:31,804
Where were you?

612
00:40:33,842 --> 00:40:36,106
Here, it's near... the airport!

613
00:40:36,578 --> 00:40:38,637
I went to see somebody off...

614
00:40:38,781 --> 00:40:40,510
So I drop by

615
00:40:41,583 --> 00:40:42,345
Hungry?

616
00:40:42,484 --> 00:40:44,850
You bought so much food to the airport?

617
00:40:46,121 --> 00:40:49,090
Well, it's cheap there. So...

618
00:40:49,959 --> 00:40:51,221
Never mind

619
00:40:51,827 --> 00:40:52,816
My sister

620
00:40:55,164 --> 00:40:56,927
Actually I come for you

621
00:40:57,800 --> 00:40:59,267
I worry if you are alright,

622
00:40:59,435 --> 00:41:00,402
so...

623
00:41:01,003 --> 00:41:03,597
I bought all these nutriment...

624
00:41:03,739 --> 00:41:05,331
for you

625
00:41:05,474 --> 00:41:07,669
I'll go after I leave them here

626
00:41:08,377 --> 00:41:11,141
You're so nice. Come on in

627
00:41:11,780 --> 00:41:13,338
You're like...

628
00:41:13,482 --> 00:41:14,176
door-keeping gods

629
00:41:14,316 --> 00:41:15,112
This is Dr. Woo

630
00:41:15,250 --> 00:41:16,342
- How are you?
- Fine, how are you?

631
00:41:16,485 --> 00:41:17,474
How are you, baby?

632
00:41:18,454 --> 00:41:20,854
Doing butterfly stroke every day

633
00:41:20,990 --> 00:41:22,924
Bang, bang, bang. Drive you nut

634
00:41:23,225 --> 00:41:24,055
You are really nice

635
00:41:24,426 --> 00:41:26,326
We live so far away and you still come

636
00:41:26,729 --> 00:41:27,525
Just drop by

637
00:41:28,163 --> 00:41:29,790
Stay for dinner, then

638
00:41:29,965 --> 00:41:30,897
Sure

639
00:41:32,067 --> 00:41:34,194
My sis needs to talk to someone

640
00:41:36,739 --> 00:41:38,297
Let me help. It's heavy

641
00:41:40,409 --> 00:41:41,433
Are you sure?

642
00:41:45,014 --> 00:41:46,276
Isn't it a bit impulsive?

643
00:41:48,984 --> 00:41:50,144
You should have...

644
00:41:50,285 --> 00:41:52,549
known before

645
00:41:53,655 --> 00:41:54,644
Years ago

646
00:41:54,790 --> 00:41:56,189
when my first patient died,

647
00:41:56,325 --> 00:41:57,815
I thought the same way

648
00:41:59,194 --> 00:42:00,456
Then I told myself:

649
00:42:00,829 --> 00:42:03,093
Many things are out of my control

650
00:42:04,066 --> 00:42:05,556
If you give up

651
00:42:05,734 --> 00:42:08,362
Then you shouldn't ever start

652
00:42:12,474 --> 00:42:13,270
Sis

653
00:42:14,009 --> 00:42:16,637
Are you hot, or just doing facial?

654
00:42:18,080 --> 00:42:19,172
Just getting to the point

655
00:42:22,851 --> 00:42:24,182
She's quite funny

656
00:42:24,553 --> 00:42:26,214
Yes. She's more simple

657
00:42:27,089 --> 00:42:27,851
How about you?

658
00:42:31,493 --> 00:42:33,017
I know what you mean

659
00:42:34,963 --> 00:42:36,658
The seniors say

660
00:42:36,832 --> 00:42:37,890
when you see patients die,

661
00:42:38,067 --> 00:42:40,126
Go see the new-born and

662
00:42:40,302 --> 00:42:41,735
you'll feel better

663
00:42:44,773 --> 00:42:46,798
But he's not just any patients

664
00:42:48,477 --> 00:42:49,409
He's Onion

665
00:42:52,147 --> 00:42:53,045
You won't understand

666
00:42:54,249 --> 00:42:55,273
I didn't believe it before

667
00:42:55,951 --> 00:42:57,316
Until it happens...

668
00:42:57,453 --> 00:42:58,818
to you

669
00:43:01,023 --> 00:43:02,251
I can't go on

670
00:43:05,127 --> 00:43:07,687
Let it out, you'll feel better

671
00:43:11,633 --> 00:43:12,759
Don't worry

672
00:43:13,435 --> 00:43:14,663
I won't just go

673
00:43:15,037 --> 00:43:16,299
I'll stay till the end of this month

674
00:43:17,372 --> 00:43:19,237
Help the new comer...

675
00:43:19,575 --> 00:43:20,507
get used to things

676
00:43:22,611 --> 00:43:23,578
I need time

677
00:43:25,914 --> 00:43:27,074
Give me time

678
00:43:27,616 --> 00:43:29,379
I can change your mind

679
00:43:31,186 --> 00:43:32,016
Thank you

680
00:43:32,721 --> 00:43:34,211
I feel much better now

681
00:43:37,659 --> 00:43:38,648
Coming, coming

682
00:43:40,329 --> 00:43:41,023
Who do you want?

683
00:43:45,534 --> 00:43:46,501
My sister?

684
00:43:56,478 --> 00:43:57,843
What a crowd today

685
00:43:58,313 --> 00:43:59,905
So...

686
00:44:00,048 --> 00:44:01,481
many people coming

687
00:44:03,252 --> 00:44:04,241
Are you dropping by too?

688
00:44:04,953 --> 00:44:06,887
No, I come for her

689
00:44:07,689 --> 00:44:08,917
I have to talk to you

690
00:44:09,258 --> 00:44:10,122
Really?

691
00:44:10,626 --> 00:44:11,422
I called you

692
00:44:11,560 --> 00:44:12,822
They said you were on leave

693
00:44:13,595 --> 00:44:14,584
Sorry about last time

694
00:44:14,997 --> 00:44:16,294
I want my indemnity

695
00:44:17,032 --> 00:44:19,000
I won't reject anything from Onion

696
00:44:19,568 --> 00:44:20,694
Fine, but...

697
00:44:20,869 --> 00:44:23,099
You are insurance broker?

698
00:44:24,106 --> 00:44:24,902
My last name's Cheuk

699
00:44:25,607 --> 00:44:26,471
Mr. Cheuk

700
00:44:27,576 --> 00:44:29,635
It's getting more and more complex

701
00:44:30,212 --> 00:44:32,442
You come so far to indemnify. Very nice

702
00:44:32,881 --> 00:44:33,870
Stay for dinner

703
00:44:35,417 --> 00:44:36,441
Sure, sure

704
00:44:43,492 --> 00:44:44,220
What is that?

705
00:44:44,760 --> 00:44:46,694
Watch it. You'll know

706
00:44:47,930 --> 00:44:48,919
I'll watch it later

707
00:44:54,937 --> 00:44:55,733
Mr. Cheuk

708
00:44:58,674 --> 00:45:00,266
Mr. Cheuk, he's calling you

709
00:45:01,009 --> 00:45:01,839
Mr. Cheuk

710
00:45:02,878 --> 00:45:04,072
You are hard-working

711
00:45:04,413 --> 00:45:06,779
Still working while on leave

712
00:45:07,983 --> 00:45:10,110
I want to settle this quick for Onion

713
00:45:11,553 --> 00:45:13,544
Dr. Woo, you work hard too

714
00:45:14,223 --> 00:45:15,121
Aren't you on leave?

715
00:45:18,560 --> 00:45:20,152
Mr. Cheuk, I think we never met

716
00:45:21,496 --> 00:45:22,929
How do you know my name?

717
00:45:25,234 --> 00:45:26,292
We never met...

718
00:45:27,102 --> 00:45:28,126
Doing insurance

719
00:45:28,303 --> 00:45:29,497
you had to know everything

720
00:45:30,105 --> 00:45:31,265
Onion died too suddenly

721
00:45:31,406 --> 00:45:32,930
We had to check people out

722
00:45:36,311 --> 00:45:39,712
Occupational disease. Blind guess

723
00:45:40,882 --> 00:45:44,318
Mr. Cheuk, you look not well

724
00:45:44,920 --> 00:45:46,319
Your lips are dark

725
00:45:47,189 --> 00:45:50,158
You better have a check

726
00:45:50,492 --> 00:45:52,426
It's professional. Not blind guess

727
00:45:58,533 --> 00:46:00,865
I queued and

728
00:46:01,003 --> 00:46:02,334
bought a cheese cake

729
00:46:02,871 --> 00:46:04,600
For dessert

730
00:46:05,007 --> 00:46:07,134
Try it. You'll feel better

731
00:46:07,876 --> 00:46:10,845
Autumn hates cheese

732
00:46:11,613 --> 00:46:13,137
She only likes fruit candies

733
00:46:13,482 --> 00:46:16,007
The octagon ones in colorful cans

734
00:46:17,653 --> 00:46:19,177
I can't believe it

735
00:46:19,755 --> 00:46:22,986
You know even that others like to eat?

736
00:46:26,061 --> 00:46:27,323
I don't eat cheese

737
00:46:31,833 --> 00:46:33,300
Why do you know?

738
00:46:33,435 --> 00:46:34,629
Are you checking on me?

739
00:46:35,170 --> 00:46:36,398
You think I killed him?

740
00:46:36,571 --> 00:46:37,663
No... How could I?

741
00:46:37,806 --> 00:46:39,364
I don't mean it

742
00:46:40,776 --> 00:46:42,175
In fact, I am...

743
00:46:44,012 --> 00:46:44,637
Here it comes again

744
00:46:44,780 --> 00:46:45,644
What's the matter with you?

745
00:46:46,081 --> 00:46:47,013
How's it going?

746
00:46:48,016 --> 00:46:49,643
Sis, do you have slippers?

747
00:46:50,519 --> 00:46:51,349
For men or women?

748
00:46:53,522 --> 00:46:54,750
Better check out...

749
00:46:54,890 --> 00:46:56,448
the nearest hospital

750
00:46:56,591 --> 00:46:57,683
Just in case...

751
00:46:59,561 --> 00:47:00,493
Autumn?

752
00:47:01,663 --> 00:47:04,689
Back in her room. She's pissed off

753
00:47:05,934 --> 00:47:07,060
I didn't mean it

754
00:47:07,469 --> 00:47:09,266
I didn't check on her. Please tell her

755
00:47:09,571 --> 00:47:10,663
Okay, okay...

756
00:47:11,506 --> 00:47:12,734
You threw...

757
00:47:12,874 --> 00:47:13,568
everything up

758
00:47:14,009 --> 00:47:15,033
Have some cheese cake

759
00:47:15,177 --> 00:47:16,075
Sis

760
00:47:16,778 --> 00:47:19,076
The doctors often suggest...

761
00:47:19,247 --> 00:47:21,010
...not to eat too rich after vomiting

762
00:47:21,483 --> 00:47:23,917
No cheese cake. You have something flat?

763
00:47:25,554 --> 00:47:26,486
Apple

764
00:47:27,656 --> 00:47:28,588
Have it

765
00:47:29,191 --> 00:47:30,749
Can we talk,

766
00:47:30,892 --> 00:47:31,688
Dr. Woo?

767
00:47:32,928 --> 00:47:33,690
Sure

768
00:47:40,435 --> 00:47:41,800
Can we donate Onion's money...

769
00:47:41,937 --> 00:47:43,461
to the hospital...

770
00:47:44,439 --> 00:47:45,497
...for ophthalmology studies?

771
00:47:45,640 --> 00:47:46,698
He wished to help

772
00:47:48,610 --> 00:47:50,942
Sure. I can suggest to the hospital...

773
00:47:51,079 --> 00:47:53,377
...to launch a fund...

774
00:47:53,915 --> 00:47:54,574
for the blind people

775
00:48:04,593 --> 00:48:06,584
I thought you really were busy,

776
00:48:06,728 --> 00:48:08,059
have no time to go to concerts

777
00:48:08,764 --> 00:48:10,425
Now I know

778
00:48:12,100 --> 00:48:13,567
I am quite jealous of him

779
00:48:15,604 --> 00:48:16,628
Sorry,

780
00:48:16,772 --> 00:48:19,206
it seems not respectful

781
00:48:20,909 --> 00:48:21,933
I think...

782
00:48:22,077 --> 00:48:23,908
he doesn't want to see you like that

783
00:48:31,086 --> 00:48:33,020
Could we go to concert tomorrow night?

784
00:48:35,557 --> 00:48:36,922
Can we talk tomorrow?

785
00:48:37,259 --> 00:48:38,453
Hope to see you tomorrow

786
00:48:41,530 --> 00:48:43,293
It's getting cold. Let's go in

787
00:48:50,372 --> 00:48:51,634
It's late. Please go

788
00:48:52,240 --> 00:48:53,673
Give Mr. Cheuk a ride, would you?

789
00:48:54,176 --> 00:48:54,972
Where's Mr. Cheuk?

790
00:49:13,495 --> 00:49:15,326
I don't know what you want

791
00:49:16,498 --> 00:49:17,465
I won't...

792
00:49:18,166 --> 00:49:20,657
let you hurt Autumn

793
00:49:23,071 --> 00:49:26,905
I don't have time. Stop the car

794
00:49:28,143 --> 00:49:29,110
You want to vomit?

795
00:49:37,719 --> 00:49:39,584
Thanks for having taken care of Onion

796
00:49:39,888 --> 00:49:40,820
Bye

797
00:49:43,792 --> 00:49:45,123
Where are you going?

798
00:49:46,595 --> 00:49:48,358
I won't let you go back and bug Autumn!

799
00:49:57,839 --> 00:49:59,067
Would you please get in?

800
00:49:59,374 --> 00:50:00,272
I won't leave

801
00:50:01,510 --> 00:50:03,068
I didn't ask you to leave

802
00:50:03,478 --> 00:50:04,877
I won't let you bother Autumn

803
00:50:05,013 --> 00:50:06,275
Let me go back with you

804
00:50:06,414 --> 00:50:07,642
Okay?

805
00:50:14,756 --> 00:50:15,688
Mr. Cheuk,

806
00:50:16,124 --> 00:50:18,354
personally I don't like you

807
00:50:20,262 --> 00:50:21,229
But...

808
00:50:21,396 --> 00:50:22,693
you are a patient to me

809
00:50:23,899 --> 00:50:25,526
You might get pneumonia,

810
00:50:25,700 --> 00:50:26,667
triggering epilepsy

811
00:50:31,206 --> 00:50:32,503
Get in, would you?

812
00:50:39,080 --> 00:50:40,172
Thank you

813
00:50:42,250 --> 00:50:43,615
I must keep an eye on you

814
00:50:45,120 --> 00:50:47,315
You broke my car

815
00:50:47,656 --> 00:50:48,884
I have to take you to the police

816
00:50:53,461 --> 00:50:54,291
You like her

817
00:50:54,729 --> 00:50:55,661
You do too

818
00:50:57,098 --> 00:50:58,065
Right

819
00:50:59,067 --> 00:51:01,865
She told me she cared about me

820
00:51:07,008 --> 00:51:08,373
You've been in our hospital?

821
00:51:09,978 --> 00:51:11,275
Did she take care of you?

822
00:51:13,348 --> 00:51:14,610
But the way I see it...

823
00:51:18,787 --> 00:51:20,652
I think you've got it all wrong

824
00:51:22,524 --> 00:51:23,923
What do you mean?

825
00:51:24,993 --> 00:51:28,690
Nurses always cares about patients

826
00:51:28,863 --> 00:51:30,262
Especially someone like Autumn

827
00:51:31,199 --> 00:51:32,131
But it's different from...

828
00:51:32,267 --> 00:51:34,394
what you think

829
00:51:34,970 --> 00:51:38,804
I am not saying this because I want her

830
00:51:39,240 --> 00:51:40,264
I hope you get it

831
00:52:14,442 --> 00:52:15,966
Didn't she read the letter?

832
00:52:16,678 --> 00:52:18,373
Will she believe it?

833
00:52:19,914 --> 00:52:22,246
Maybe she never ever like me

834
00:52:22,384 --> 00:52:23,783
She just pities me

835
00:52:24,119 --> 00:52:28,988
I am just a common patient to her

836
00:52:30,191 --> 00:52:33,160
I know you want me to regret, right?

837
00:52:34,229 --> 00:52:36,823
How could angels be so unkind?

838
00:53:02,757 --> 00:53:03,621
Good morning

839
00:53:04,993 --> 00:53:06,290
- Good morning
- Staying late?

840
00:53:07,062 --> 00:53:08,859
No, I have a date with you

841
00:53:09,030 --> 00:53:10,998
Not sure if I can get up. So I stay

842
00:53:11,800 --> 00:53:12,767
Where is he?

843
00:53:12,934 --> 00:53:13,559
Who?

844
00:53:13,735 --> 00:53:15,566
Mr. Cheuk! My car's locked

845
00:53:16,037 --> 00:53:16,833
He didn't leave?

846
00:53:18,473 --> 00:53:19,667
Never mind. I'll make some coffee

847
00:53:21,176 --> 00:53:22,643
- Take a seat
- Okay

848
00:53:22,777 --> 00:53:24,404
Could you give me a ride later?

849
00:53:24,779 --> 00:53:25,404
Where to?

850
00:53:26,181 --> 00:53:28,411
Anywhere, take a break, go to concert

851
00:53:29,851 --> 00:53:30,875
Sure

852
00:53:46,401 --> 00:53:47,333
Did you read it?

853
00:53:48,136 --> 00:53:50,036
You wait a whole night here for that?

854
00:53:51,539 --> 00:53:52,437
I read it

855
00:53:53,374 --> 00:53:55,274
Good! You finally got it?

856
00:53:56,478 --> 00:53:57,945
I am sorry... Mr. Angel

857
00:53:58,079 --> 00:53:59,307
I was irrational

858
00:53:59,447 --> 00:54:00,505
You didn't hear a thing

859
00:54:00,648 --> 00:54:01,580
Are you alright?

860
00:54:03,785 --> 00:54:04,877
Did you really read it?

861
00:54:05,487 --> 00:54:06,476
Didn't miss anything?

862
00:54:06,755 --> 00:54:08,780
I don't know what's in your apology card

863
00:54:09,991 --> 00:54:12,152
And this tape's blank

864
00:54:13,194 --> 00:54:14,684
But I accept your apology

865
00:54:15,029 --> 00:54:16,758
Please proceed with my indemnity

866
00:54:17,065 --> 00:54:18,191
and stay away from me afterward

867
00:54:26,274 --> 00:54:26,831
If Mr. Cheuk ever comes...

868
00:54:26,975 --> 00:54:27,942
to the hospital again

869
00:54:28,076 --> 00:54:28,701
Do pay us a visit

870
00:54:28,843 --> 00:54:29,571
We are in charge of ophthalmology

871
00:54:29,944 --> 00:54:32,344
I know, I specialize in the blind

872
00:54:33,348 --> 00:54:36,408
I'm always there. So I understand them

873
00:54:37,919 --> 00:54:39,910
Sometimes I even touch their books

874
00:54:40,688 --> 00:54:42,212
like onion's point diary

875
00:54:43,825 --> 00:54:45,816
I know a lot from that

876
00:54:45,960 --> 00:54:46,984
Diary?

877
00:54:47,295 --> 00:54:48,785
I didn't know she'd react that way

878
00:54:49,297 --> 00:54:51,060
Even ask me out tonight

879
00:54:51,800 --> 00:54:52,767
She wants...

