01:22:02,435 --> 01:22:05,131
I am so careless

1169
01:22:05,505 --> 01:22:06,802
I didn't realize

1170
01:22:06,939 --> 01:22:08,804
until I see all the proofs

1171
01:22:09,842 --> 01:22:11,776
I am so dumb

1172
01:22:16,682 --> 01:22:19,947
Are you going now?

1173
01:22:22,655 --> 01:22:25,920
Yes, I had to

1174
01:22:27,026 --> 01:22:28,516
You'll never see me again

1175
01:22:29,462 --> 01:22:31,930
I am not anyone...

1176
01:22:32,832 --> 01:22:35,858
Forget it, Onion is dead

1177
01:22:36,869 --> 01:22:38,427
He never comes back

1178
01:22:39,505 --> 01:22:41,132
You must take care yourself

1179
01:22:42,308 --> 01:22:44,401
Go! Go!

1180
01:22:44,544 --> 01:22:45,442
Okay!

1181
01:22:46,412 --> 01:22:48,471
Excuse me, please wait

1182
01:22:49,115 --> 01:22:51,583
I have one last question

1183
01:22:54,554 --> 01:22:55,987
If you were him,

1184
01:22:57,023 --> 01:22:59,617
Seeing the one he loves so painful

1185
01:23:00,993 --> 01:23:02,358
What do you want her to do?

1186
01:23:08,134 --> 01:23:12,332
Forget me and love someone else

1187
01:23:14,407 --> 01:23:16,898
Live happily again

1188
01:23:17,510 --> 01:23:19,740
Let go of the painful memories

1189
01:23:21,080 --> 01:23:23,048
Okay! I'll tell him now

1190
01:23:23,749 --> 01:23:25,182
I've forgot his death

1191
01:23:25,985 --> 01:23:27,646
I won't carry the pains with me!

1192
01:23:29,121 --> 01:23:30,782
I will love someone again

1193
01:23:32,191 --> 01:23:34,125
And that's you!

1194
01:23:35,861 --> 01:23:37,123
But he stays...

1195
01:23:37,263 --> 01:23:39,493
in my heart

1196
01:23:41,033 --> 01:23:43,399
It's fine if you don't admit it

1197
01:23:44,604 --> 01:23:47,129
I don't care if you're Cheuk

1198
01:23:48,741 --> 01:23:53,337
But I know, I always love...

1199
01:23:53,646 --> 01:23:55,204
Who is the one I always love

1200
01:23:57,950 --> 01:24:00,043
Onion, you listen up

1201
01:24:00,353 --> 01:24:02,412
I love this person in front of me!

1202
01:24:05,758 --> 01:24:07,191
Don't go away

1203
01:24:09,195 --> 01:24:11,356
Don't leave me alone...

1204
01:24:51,937 --> 01:24:52,494
This is...

1205
01:24:52,638 --> 01:24:54,071
the meteor shower night

1206
01:24:54,407 --> 01:24:56,705
China is the best place to see it

1207
01:24:57,209 --> 01:24:59,336
I'll be here with you tonight

1208
01:25:00,346 --> 01:25:01,608
Onion told me

1209
01:25:02,448 --> 01:25:05,042
Your first wish was that he could watch

1210
01:25:05,184 --> 01:25:07,982
the meteor shower with you

1211
01:25:10,756 --> 01:25:12,155
It's the same you watch it with me

1212
01:25:14,694 --> 01:25:16,525
There's no meteor shower yet

1213
01:25:17,997 --> 01:25:20,761
You're a good person. God will help you

1214
01:25:21,534 --> 01:25:24,332
Then help me keep Onion!

1215
01:25:24,704 --> 01:25:26,672
Stay with me forever, would you?

1216
01:25:29,642 --> 01:25:31,769
That's my second wish

1217
01:25:36,182 --> 01:25:40,016
Onion had a second wish too

1218
01:25:41,987 --> 01:25:45,013
But it's already impossible...

1219
01:25:46,992 --> 01:25:48,391
It's 2:30 in the morning

1220
01:25:48,527 --> 01:25:49,687
Ten minutes to go...

1221
01:25:49,829 --> 01:25:52,093
for the peak hour

1222
01:25:52,832 --> 01:25:54,163
I wonder if Cheuk...

1223
01:25:54,300 --> 01:25:55,733
...will call again tonight

1224
01:26:03,315 --> 01:26:05,834
Hello, I'm Cheuk

1225
01:26:06,912 --> 01:26:09,472
I appreciate people caring about me

1226
01:26:10,249 --> 01:26:11,546
I want...

1227
01:26:11,684 --> 01:26:14,710
to say something to my love

1228
01:26:15,020 --> 01:26:16,385
Why not say it directly to her?

1229
01:26:17,857 --> 01:26:18,619
Because...

1230
01:26:20,860 --> 01:26:22,293
of fate

1231
01:26:23,395 --> 01:26:25,420
When I didn't expect anything

1232
01:26:27,032 --> 01:26:28,795
I owned her love unexpectedly

1233
01:26:30,503 --> 01:26:32,903
When I wanted her...

1234
01:26:33,773 --> 01:26:35,434
or made a choice

1235
01:26:36,442 --> 01:26:39,036
she went away, disliked me

1236
01:26:40,312 --> 01:26:41,779
I am leaving soon

1237
01:26:42,915 --> 01:26:45,213
Keeping the most unforgettable moment

1238
01:26:46,652 --> 01:26:49,780
Laughter or tears

1239
01:26:50,890 --> 01:26:52,448
I hope every bits of memory

1240
01:26:53,659 --> 01:26:55,524
be with the one I love most

1241
01:26:56,061 --> 01:27:00,464
Carry on with her life. Be strong...

1242
01:27:04,436 --> 01:27:07,564
Five days is very short

1243
01:27:08,941 --> 01:27:11,034
I want to tell friends in the air

1244
01:27:12,778 --> 01:27:14,939
Hold what you have

1245
01:27:16,315 --> 01:27:20,274
Now, or in the future

1246
01:27:21,654 --> 01:27:23,451
Even if it slips away...

1247
01:27:25,391 --> 01:27:27,018
I have no regret of this life

1248
01:27:31,163 --> 01:27:33,597
That's so touching

1249
01:27:34,300 --> 01:27:35,824
If only you were my boyfriend

1250
01:27:36,502 --> 01:27:38,629
May I offer any help?

1251
01:27:44,410 --> 01:27:45,672
