1252
01:27:46,579 --> 01:27:48,604
for my love?

1253
01:27:55,988 --> 01:28:00,254
Sure. Let's go for the meteor shower

1254
01:28:01,560 --> 01:28:02,822
Before I hang up

1255
01:28:04,530 --> 01:28:07,226
I hope everyone close your eyes again

1256
01:28:08,334 --> 01:28:09,392
Feel the one...

1257
01:28:09,535 --> 01:28:10,399
by your side with your heart

1258
01:28:12,104 --> 01:28:15,767
You'll have better feeling

1259
01:28:52,645 --> 01:28:53,976
Meteor shower!

1260
01:29:05,391 --> 01:29:08,087
I've fulfilled my first wish

1261
01:29:12,932 --> 01:29:14,058
Make a wish, quick

1262
01:29:22,408 --> 01:29:23,466
No...

1263
01:29:25,344 --> 01:29:28,040
I did last time, you still have to go

1264
01:29:32,751 --> 01:29:33,342
Come back

1265
01:29:33,485 --> 01:29:36,454
when the meteor showers

1266
01:29:51,637 --> 01:29:54,765
"Wait for you"

1267
01:30:56,402 --> 01:30:58,495
Finally, I know what is meteor shower

1268
01:30:59,938 --> 01:31:02,805
The tears of the sky...
